<h1>Timezone Bot&nbsp;&#x2013; <code>/timezone-dropdown</code> help</h1>

<p>
    The basic syntax is the following: <code>/timezone-dropdown [options: timezone1,timezone2,timezone3]</code>.
    The timezones expected here are the same as the <code>/timezone</code> command.
</p>

<b>Command:</b>
